@page "/"
<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="container p-0">

    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 5px;">
        <img src="logo-pda.png" style="max-width: 150px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
    </div>

    <h1 class="display-4 text-center" style="margin-top: 5px;">About the Project</h1> 

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p class="lead text-center" style="margin-top: 5px;">
                This project will serve as an online calculator that evaluates if a university has reached its
                Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs).
            </p>

            <hr />

            <h4 class="mt-3 text-center" style="margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 8px;">Our Goal</h4>
            <p>
                Our goal is to create an accessible and user-friendly tool for university administrators and stakeholders
                to easily evaluate and track their progress toward achieving these important goals.
            </p>

            <hr />

            <h4 class="mt-3 text-center" style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 8px;">Technology Stack</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 3px;">
                This project was developed using the following technologies:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Blazor</strong> - A framework for building interactive web UIs using C# instead of JavaScript.</li>
                <li><strong>C#</strong> - The primary programming language used for the project's backend logic.</li>
                <li><strong>.NET 8</strong> - The latest version of the .NET framework, offering improved performance and features.</li>
                <li><strong>Bootstrap</strong> - A popular CSS framework used to ensure a responsive and visually appealing design.</li>
                <li><strong>GitHub</strong> - The complete project is available on GitHub, one of the most popular version control 
                    platforms. Click the link in the page footer to explore the project.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <hr />
            <h4 class="mt-3 text-center" style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 8px;">Website Structure</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 3px;">
                The website has 3 main pages:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Home</strong> - This page, showing information about the development of this project.</li>
                <li><strong>About SDGs</strong> - A page diving deeper into what Sustainable Development Goals are. </li>
                <li><strong>Calculator</strong> - A page used to calculate a university's degree of compliance with the SDGs. </li>
            </ul>
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top: 50px;">
        
    </p>
</div>

